🧠 2. Agents (Multi‑Agent From Day One)
Router Agent

    Classifies intent

    Chooses model tier (Phi‑3 Mini or Llama 3.1 8B)

    Routes to Planner

    Enforces ingestion‑only external calls

Planner Agent

    Breaks tasks into steps

    Decides which tools/skills to use

    Escalates to Llama 3.1 8B for complex tasks

    Can request “heavy mode” manually

Executor Agent

    Validates tool schemas

    Runs tools

    Handles errors

    Returns structured results

Memory Agent

    SQLite storage

    Embeddings (MiniLM‑L6‑v2)

    Workflow state

    Semantic search

Persona Agent

    Formats responses

    Adds tone

    Prepares text for TTS

