🎤 4. Voice Pipeline
Wake‑Word

    Vosk listens continuously

    Low CPU overhead

Speech‑to‑Text

    Whisper (tiny or base)

    Converts audio → text

    Sends text directly to Router Agent

Text‑to‑Speech

    Piper TTS

    Fast streaming

    Ideal for “JARVIS‑snappy” responses

